<item>
            <title>[SOLR-7545] SOLR_HOST parameter not honoured in bin/solr and SolrCLI</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7545</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It seems there are a few places in bin/solr (and maybe SolrCLI class?) where localhost is hardcoded, and hence the SOLR_HOST parameter isn&apos;t taking effect. Will add a patch to fix this shortly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
